## 5. Rollback instructions

`controllers/mission_manager.py` is untracked in git, so there's no commit to revert. To roll back:
- Re-apply the diff in reverse (remove `_MODE_FILENAMES`, `_load_experts`, the `_load_experts()` call in `load()`, and restore the original docstrings), or
- Restore from your own backup/editor history if you have one, since there's no git history for this file yet.

`models/experts/.gitkeep` can simply be deleted; it has no effect on behavior (the directory check in `_load_experts` just skips loading if the dir doesn't exist or is empty).
